{"data":[{"name":"83:1","price":"विनाश है नाप-तौल में कमी करने वालों के लिए।","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ لِّلۡمُطَفِّفِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5849,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun lil'muṭaffifīna ","translations":["Woe","to those who give less","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","lil'muṭaffifīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,800],[2,800,4755]]}},{"name":"83:2","price":"वे लोग कि जब लोगों से नापकर लेते हैं, तो पूरा लेते हैं।","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ إِذَا ٱكۡتَالُواْ عَلَى ٱلنَّاسِ يَسۡتَوۡفُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5850,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhīna idhā ik'tālū ʿalā al-nāsi yastawfūna ","translations":["Those who","when","they take a measure","from","the people","they take in full","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhīna","idhā","ik'tālū","ʿalā","al-nāsi","yastawfūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1220],[2,1220,1620],[3,1620,2620],[4,2620,3010],[5,3010,4740],[6,4740,7945]]}},{"name":"83:3","price":"और जब उन्हें नापकर या तौलकर देते हैं, तो कम देते हैं।","arabic":"وَإِذَا كَالُوهُمۡ أَو وَّزَنُوهُمۡ يُخۡسِرُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5851,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā kālūhum aw wazanūhum yukh'sirūna ","translations":["But when","they give by measure (to) them","or","they weigh (for) them","they give less","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","kālūhum","aw","wazanūhum","yukh'sirūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,2210],[3,2210,2500],[4,2500,3750],[5,3750,6895]]}},{"name":"83:4","price":"क्या वे लोग विश्वास नहीं रखते कि वे (मरने के बाद) उठाए जाने वाले हैं?","arabic":"أَلَا يَظُنُّ أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ أَنَّهُم مَّبۡعُوثُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5852,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"alā yaẓunnu ulāika annahum mabʿūthūna ","translations":["Do not","think","those","that they","(will be) resurrected","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["alā","yaẓunnu","ulāika","annahum","mabʿūthūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,2400],[3,2400,4610],[4,4610,6470],[5,6470,10305]]}},{"name":"83:5","price":"एक बहुत बड़े दिन के लिए।","arabic":"لِيَوۡمٍ عَظِيمٖ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5853,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"liyawmin ʿaẓīmin ","translations":["For a Day","Great","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["liyawmin","ʿaẓīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1030],[2,1030,4045]]}},{"name":"83:6","price":"जिस दिन लोग सर्व संसार के पालनहार के सामने खड़े होंगे।[1]","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَقُومُ ٱلنَّاسُ لِرَبِّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5854,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1. (1-6) इस सूरत की प्रथम छह आयतों में इसी व्यवसायिक विश्वास घात पर पकड़ की गई है कि न्याय तो यह है कि अपने लिए अन्याय नहीं चाहते, तो दूसरों के साथ न्याय करो। और इस रोग का निवारण अल्लाह के भय तथा परलोक पर विश्वास ही से हो सकता है। क्योंकि इस स्थिति में अमानतदारी एक नीति ही नहीं, बल्कि धार्मिक कर्तव्य होगा औ इस पर स्थित रहना लाभ तथा हानि पर निर्भर नहीं रहेगा।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma yaqūmu al-nāsu lirabbi al-ʿālamīna ","translations":["(The) Day","will stand","mankind","before (the) Lord","(of) the worlds","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","yaqūmu","al-nāsu","lirabbi","al-ʿālamīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,620],[2,620,1490],[3,1490,3130],[4,3130,3940],[5,3940,7905]]}},{"name":"83:7","price":"हरगिज़ नहीं, निःसंदेह दुराचारियों का कर्म-पत्र \"सिज्जीन\" में है।","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّ كِتَٰبَ ٱلۡفُجَّارِ لَفِي سِجِّينٖ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5855,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā inna kitāba al-fujāri lafī sijjīnin ","translations":["Nay","Indeed","(the) record","(of) the wicked","(is) surely in","Sijjin","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","inna","kitāba","al-fujāri","lafī","sijjīnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2559],[2,2559,3699],[3,3699,4509],[4,4509,5769],[5,5769,6329],[6,6329,10014]]}},{"name":"83:8","price":"और तुम क्या जानो कि 'सिज्जीन' क्या है?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا سِجِّينٞ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5856,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā sijjīnun ","translations":["And what","can make you know","what","(is) Sijjin","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","sijjīnun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2320],[2,2320,3380],[3,3380,3720],[4,3720,7575]]}},{"name":"83:9","price":"वह एक लिखित पुस्तक है।","arabic":"كِتَٰبٞ مَّرۡقُومٞ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5857,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"kitābun marqūmun ","translations":["A book","written","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["kitābun","marqūmun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,5135]]}},{"name":"83:10","price":"उस दिन झुठलाने वालों के लिए विनाश है।","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5858,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun yawma-idhin lil'mukadhibīna ","translations":["Woe","that Day","to the deniers","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","yawma-idhin","lil'mukadhibīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1680],[2,1680,2660],[3,2660,6475]]}},{"name":"83:11","price":"जो बदले के दिन को झुठलाते हैं।","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ يُكَذِّبُونَ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5859,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhīna yukadhibūna biyawmi al-dīni ","translations":["Those who","deny","(the) Day","(of) the Judgment","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhīna","yukadhibūna","biyawmi","al-dīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1260],[2,1260,2720],[3,2720,3540],[4,3540,6215]]}},{"name":"83:12","price":"तथा उसे केवल वही झुठलाता है, जो सीमा का उल्लंघन करने वाला, बड़ा पापी है।","arabic":"وَمَا يُكَذِّبُ بِهِۦٓ إِلَّا كُلُّ مُعۡتَدٍ أَثِيمٍ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5860,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā yukadhibu bihi illā kullu muʿ'tadin athīmin ","translations":["And not","can deny","[of] it","except","every","transgressor","sinful","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","yukadhibu","bihi","illā","kullu","muʿ'tadin","athīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,700],[2,700,1750],[3,1750,3770],[4,3770,4550],[5,4550,5240],[6,5240,6210],[7,6210,9285]]}},{"name":"83:13","price":"जब उसके सामने हमारी आयतों को पढ़ा जाता है, तो कहता है : यह पहले लोगों की कहानियाँ हैं।","arabic":"إِذَا تُتۡلَىٰ عَلَيۡهِ ءَايَٰتُنَا قَالَ أَسَٰطِيرُ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5861,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"idhā tut'lā ʿalayhi āyātunā qāla asāṭīru al-awalīna ","translations":["When","are recited","to him","Our Verses","he says","Stories","(of) the former (people)","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["idhā","tut'lā","ʿalayhi","āyātunā","qāla","asāṭīru","al-awalīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,740],[2,740,1550],[3,1550,2400],[4,2400,3830],[5,3830,4550],[6,4550,5740],[7,5740,9605]]}},{"name":"83:14","price":"हरगिज़ नहीं, बल्कि जो कुछ वे कमाते थे, वह ज़ंग बनकर उनके दिलों पर छा गया है।","arabic":"كَلَّاۖ بَلۡۜ رَانَ عَلَىٰ قُلُوبِهِم مَّا كَانُواْ يَكۡسِبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5862,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā bal rāna ʿalā qulūbihim mā kānū yaksibūna ","translations":["Nay","But","(the) stain has covered","[over]","their hearts","(for) what","they used to","earn","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","bal","rāna","ʿalā","qulūbihim","mā","kānū","yaksibūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,940],[2,940,1400],[3,1400,2260],[4,2260,2960],[5,2960,4540],[6,4540,5520],[7,5520,6390],[8,6390,9485]]}},{"name":"83:15","price":"हरगिज़ नहीं, निश्चय वे उस दिन अपने पालनहार (के दर्शन) से रोक दिए जाएँगे।","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهُمۡ عَن رَّبِّهِمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لَّمَحۡجُوبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5863,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā innahum ʿan rabbihim yawma-idhin lamaḥjūbūna ","translations":["Nay","Indeed, they","from","their Lord","that Day","surely will be partitioned","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","innahum","ʿan","rabbihim","yawma-idhin","lamaḥjūbūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2490],[2,2490,4080],[3,4080,4320],[4,4320,5570],[5,5570,6730],[6,6730,10635]]}},{"name":"83:16","price":"फिर निःसंदेह वे अवश्य जहन्नम में प्रवेश करने वाले हैं।","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّهُمۡ لَصَالُواْ ٱلۡجَحِيمِ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5864,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma innahum laṣālū al-jaḥīmi ","translations":["Then","indeed, they","(surely) will burn","(in) the Hellfire","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","innahum","laṣālū","al-jaḥīmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1500],[2,1500,3430],[3,3430,4280],[4,4280,7255]]}},{"name":"83:17","price":"फिर कहा जाएगा : यही है, जिसे तुम झुठलाया करते थे।[2]","arabic":"ثُمَّ يُقَالُ هَٰذَا ٱلَّذِي كُنتُم بِهِۦ تُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5865,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"2. (7-17) इन आयतों में कुकर्मियों के दुष्परिणाम का विवरण दिया गया है। तथा यह बताया गया है कि उनके कुकर्म पहले ही से अपराध पत्रों में अंकित किए जा रहे हैं। तथा वे परलोक में कड़ी यातना का सामना करेंगे। और नरक में झोंक दिए जाएँगे। \"सिज्जीन\" से अभिप्राय, एक जगह है जहाँ पर काफ़िरों, अत्याचारियों और मुश्रिकों के कुकर्म पत्र तथा प्राण एकत्र किए जाते हैं। दिलों का लोहमल, पापों की कालिमा को कहा गया है। पाप अंतरात्मा को अंधकार बना देते हैं, तो सत्य को स्वीकार करने की स्वभाविक योग्यता खो देते हैं।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma yuqālu hādhā alladhī kuntum bihi tukadhibūna ","translations":["Then","it will be said","This","(is) what","you used to","[of it]","deny","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","yuqālu","hādhā","alladhī","kuntum","bihi","tukadhibūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,2120],[3,2120,2710],[4,2710,3610],[5,3610,5090],[6,5090,6340],[7,6340,6920],[8,6920,10425]]}},{"name":"83:18","price":"हरगिज़ नहीं, निःसंदेह नेक लोगों का कर्म-पत्र निश्चय \"इल्लिय्यीन\" में है।","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّ كِتَٰبَ ٱلۡأَبۡرَارِ لَفِي عِلِّيِّينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5866,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā inna kitāba al-abrāri lafī ʿilliyyīna ","translations":["Nay","Indeed","(the) record","(of) the righteous","(will be) surely in","Illiyin","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","inna","kitāba","al-abrāri","lafī","ʿilliyyīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2320],[2,2320,3620],[3,3620,4420],[4,4420,5770],[5,5770,6380],[6,6380,9705]]}},{"name":"83:19","price":"और तुम क्या जानो कि 'इल्लिय्यीन' क्या है?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا عِلِّيُّونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5867,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā ʿilliyyūna ","translations":["And what","can make you know","what","(is) Illiyun","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","ʿilliyyūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2050],[2,2050,3080],[3,3080,3520],[4,3520,7145]]}},{"name":"83:20","price":"वह एक लिखित पुस्तक है।","arabic":"كِتَٰبٞ مَّرۡقُومٞ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5868,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"kitābun marqūmun ","translations":["A book","written","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["kitābun","marqūmun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,880],[2,880,4825]]}},{"name":"83:21","price":"जिसके पास समीपवर्ती (फरिश्ते) उपस्थित रहते हैं।","arabic":"يَشۡهَدُهُ ٱلۡمُقَرَّبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5869,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"yashhaduhu al-muqarabūna ","translations":["Witness it","those brought near","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["yashhaduhu","al-muqarabūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1030],[2,1030,4615]]}},{"name":"83:22","price":"निःसंदेह नेक लोग बड़ी नेमत (आनंद) में होंगे।","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلۡأَبۡرَارَ لَفِي نَعِيمٍ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5870,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"inna al-abrāra lafī naʿīmin ","translations":["Indeed","the righteous","(will be) surely in","bliss","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","al-abrāra","lafī","naʿīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1530],[2,1530,2830],[3,2830,3410],[4,3410,6265]]}},{"name":"83:23","price":"तख़्तों पर (बैठे) देख रहे होंगे।","arabic":"عَلَى ٱلۡأَرَآئِكِ يَنظُرُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5871,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿalā al-arāiki yanẓurūna ","translations":["On","thrones","observing","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿalā","al-arāiki","yanẓurūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,640],[2,640,3379],[3,3379,7274]]}},{"name":"83:24","price":"तुम उनके चेहरों पर नेमत की ताज़गी का आभास करोगे।","arabic":"تَعۡرِفُ فِي وُجُوهِهِمۡ نَضۡرَةَ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5872,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"taʿrifu 