}},{"name":"83:28","price":"वह एक स्रोत है, जिससे समीपवर्ती लोग पिएँगे।[3]","arabic":"عَيۡنٗا يَشۡرَبُ بِهَا ٱلۡمُقَرَّبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5876,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"3. (18-28) इन आयतों में बताया गया है कि सदाचारियों के कर्म ऊँचे पत्रों में अंकित किए जा रहे हैं जो फ़रिश्तों के पास सुरक्षित हैं। और वे स्वर्ग में सुख के साथ रहेंगे। \"इल्लिय्यीन\" से अभिप्राय, जन्नत में एक जगह है। जहाँ पर नेक लोगों के कर्म पत्र तथा प्राण एकत्र किए जाते हैं। वहाँ पर समीपवर्ती फ़रिश्ते उपस्थित रहते हैं।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿaynan yashrabu bihā al-muqarabūna ","translations":["A spring","will drink","from it","those brought near","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿaynan","yashrabu","bihā","al-muqarabūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,680],[2,680,2640],[3,2640,3010],[4,3010,6825]]}},{"name":"83:29","price":"निःसंदेह जो लोग अपराधी हैं, वे (दुनिया में) ईमान लाने वालों पर हँसा करते थे।","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ أَجۡرَمُواْ كَانُواْ مِنَ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ يَضۡحَكُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5877,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"inna alladhīna ajramū kānū mina alladhīna āmanū yaḍḥakūna ","translations":["Indeed","those who","committed crimes","used to","at","those who","believed","laugh","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","alladhīna","ajramū","kānū","mina","alladhīna","āmanū","yaḍḥakūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1480],[2,1480,2520],[3,2520,3530],[4,3530,4400],[5,4400,4740],[6,4740,5790],[7,5790,6870],[8,6870,10255]]}},{"name":"83:30","price":"और जब वे उनके पास से गुज़रते, तो आपस में आँखों से इशारे किया करते थे।","arabic":"وَإِذَا مَرُّواْ بِهِمۡ يَتَغَامَزُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5878,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā marrū bihim yataghāmazūna ","translations":["And when","they passed","by them","they winked at one another","(30)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","marrū","bihim","yataghāmazūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,1800],[3,1800,2380],[4,2380,5765]]}},{"name":"83:31","price":"और जब अपने घर वालों की ओर लौटते, तो (मोमिनों के परिहास का) आनंद लेते हुए लौटते थे।","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱنقَلَبُوٓاْ إِلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهِمُ ٱنقَلَبُواْ فَكِهِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5879,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā inqalabū ilā ahlihimu inqalabū fakihīna ","translations":["And when","they returned","to","their people","they would return","jesting","(31)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","inqalabū","ilā","ahlihimu","inqalabū","fakihīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,610],[2,610,3700],[3,3700,5660],[4,5660,6650],[5,6650,8320],[6,8320,11335]]}},{"name":"83:32","price":"और जब वे उन (मोमिनों) को देखते, तो कहते थे : निःसंदेह ये लोग निश्चय भटके हुए हैं।","arabic":"وَإِذَا رَأَوۡهُمۡ قَالُوٓاْ إِنَّ هَٰٓؤُلَآءِ لَضَآلُّونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5880,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā ra-awhum qālū inna hāulāi laḍāllūna ","translations":["And when","they saw them","they said","Indeed","these","surely have gone astray","(32)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","ra-awhum","qālū","inna","hāulāi","laḍāllūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1850],[3,1850,3850],[4,3850,5100],[5,5100,8900],[6,8900,15075]]}},{"name":"83:33","price":"हालाँकि वे उनपर निरीक्षक बनाकर नहीं भेजे गए थे।","arabic":"وَمَآ أُرۡسِلُواْ عَلَيۡهِمۡ حَٰفِظِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5881,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā ur'silū ʿalayhim ḥāfiẓīna ","translations":["But not","they had been sent","over them","(as) guardians","(33)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","ur'silū","ʿalayhim","ḥāfiẓīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2440],[2,2440,3380],[3,3380,4410],[4,4410,7615]]}},{"name":"83:34","price":"तो आज वे लोग जो ईमान लाए, काफ़िरों पर हँस रहे हैं।","arabic":"فَٱلۡيَوۡمَ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ مِنَ ٱلۡكُفَّارِ يَضۡحَكُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5882,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fal-yawma alladhīna āmanū mina al-kufāri yaḍḥakūna ","translations":["So today","those who","believed ","at","the disbelievers","they will laugh","(34)"],"transliterationArr":["fal-yawma","alladhīna","āmanū","mina","al-kufāri","yaḍḥakūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1040],[2,1040,2110],[3,2110,3220],[4,3220,3560],[5,3560,4770],[6,4770,8485]]}},{"name":"83:35","price":"तख़्तों पर बैठे देख रहे हैं।","arabic":"عَلَى ٱلۡأَرَآئِكِ يَنظُرُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5883,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿalā al-arāiki yanẓurūna ","translations":["On","the thrones","observing","(35)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿalā","al-arāiki","yanẓurūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,490],[2,490,3290],[3,3290,7695]]}},{"name":"83:36","price":"क्या काफ़िरों को उसका बदला मिल गया, जो वे किया करते थे?[4]","arabic":"هَلۡ ثُوِّبَ ٱلۡكُفَّارُ مَا كَانُواْ يَفۡعَلُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5884,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"4. (29-36) इन आयतों में बताया गया है कि परलोक में कर्मों का फल दिया जाएगा, तो सांसारिक परिस्थितियाँ बदल जाएँगी। संसार में तो सब के लिए अल्लाह की दया है, परंतु न्याय के दिन जो अपने सुख सुविधा पर गर्व करते थे और जिन निर्धन मुसलमानों को देखकर आँखें मारते थे, वहाँ पर वही उनके दुष्परिणाम को देख कर प्रसन्न होंगे। अंतिम आयत में विश्वासहीनों के दुष्परिणाम को उनका कर्म कहा गया है। जिसमें यह संकेत है कि अच्छा फल और कुफल स्वयं इमसान के अपने कर्मों का स्वभाविक प्रभाव होगा।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"hal thuwwiba al-kufāru mā kānū yafʿalūna ","translation